Name: Claude: Check R Logs
Description: Analyse selected R log output with Claude. Identifies errors, warnings, root causes and fixes — including silent issues common in clinical programming.
Binding: addin_check_logs
Interactive: false

Name: Claude: Inspect Data
Description: Review a data frame for CDISC ADaM/SDTM data quality issues. Select a variable name or type it when prompted. Sends structural metadata only — no patient data.
Binding: addin_inspect_data
Interactive: false

Name: Claude: Fix R Warnings
Description: Select a warning/error message for explanation and fix, or select R code to have it corrected in-place.
Binding: addin_fix_warnings
Interactive: false

Name: Claude: Review SAP Section
Description: Review selected SAP text against ICH E9 and CDISC ADaM standards. Flags ambiguities, missing specifications, and questions to raise before programming begins.
Binding: addin_review_sap
Interactive: false

Name: Claude: Generate Job Config
Description: Analyse the active R script and generate a recommended Domino job configuration including hardware tier, environment variables, and parallelisation opportunities.
Binding: addin_generate_job_config
Interactive: false
